*** matplotlib package 설치. (virtualenv, pip3)
 - after activate virtualenv,
  pip3 install --upgrade matplotlib

*** tkinter package(python3-tk) package 설치. (virtualenv & host 구분없음. 동시에 사용가능)
 - sudo apt-get install python3-tk


*** scipy package install
 pip install --user numpy scipy matplotlib ipython jupyter pandas sympy nose

*** virtualenv install on Ubuntu
 sudo apt-get install python3-pip python3-dev python-virtualenv


*** python3 install through virtualenv
 0. $ sudo apt-get install python3-pip python3-dev python-virtualenv # for Python 3.n

 1. 
 virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3 py3env
 source py3env/bin/activate
 pip install package-name 

 2.
 virtualenv --system-site-packages -p python3 targetDirectory # for Python 3.n

 3. 
 python3 -m venv tutorial-env
 source tutorial-env/bin/activate
